"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cedcbe3b92f9c68852a89aded28085a7ae819a","tid":41741,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"唔該哂大家<br />\n我自己都google緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e50ad8a0160f9ec5fdfc3107e958d41e78e767a","tid":41741,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇得醫<br />\n一直覺得食藥嘅所謂控制, 只係食到你個人呆吓呆吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪食過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193eeb732e42fda7fcb0e49bd7e609015b8d74b6","tid":41741,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>精神科，小學証實之後開始一直睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以分享下食完藥係咪會好左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見人見智喇，我覺得心理作用大啲<br />\n不過真係冇咁易分心，係有用嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分心都會好專心咁分心<br />\n（啫係完全轉咗個專注力落另一件事上）"},{"pid":"6f05f6c77a5e37a94114f77ca109984106e0f908","tid":41741,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇得醫<br />\n一直覺得食藥嘅所謂控制, 只係食到你個人呆吓呆吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係，有時唔係做緊嘢就會個人呆咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時時做下都會呆咗一陣"},{"pid":"f35a6d4af8004fac089791f3a5a2c75aabba021b","tid":41741,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇得醫<br />\n一直覺得食藥嘅所謂控制, 只係食到你個人呆吓呆吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪食過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇食過<br />\n但以前工作需要, 接觸過好多呢類細路, 食咗藥只係呆到分唔到心 <br />\n<br />\n不過你可以試吓睇吓點先嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細路就話冇得揀唔食, <br />\n但你話到事啦嘛, 食完覺得唔啱咪唔食囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd603db224b53e6d27c9a1137931e4fa5fae9256","tid":41741,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>精神科，小學証實之後開始一直睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以分享下食完藥係咪會好左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見人見智喇，我覺得心理作用大啲<br />\n不過真係冇咁易分心，係有用嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分心都會好專心咁分心<br />\n（啫係完全轉咗個專注力落另一件事上）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大獲.. 咁咪極度唔專心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc123096b598b747cf169ad18a47f5a346368b4","tid":41741,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇得醫<br />\n一直覺得食藥嘅所謂控制, 只係食到你個人呆吓呆吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪食過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇食過<br />\n但以前工作需要, 接觸過好多呢類細路, 食咗藥只係呆到分唔到心 <br />\n<br />\n不過你可以試吓睇吓點先嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細路就話冇得揀唔食, <br />\n但你話到事啦嘛, 食完覺得唔啱咪唔食囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會想試左先"},{"pid":"3bcccdd38617d02aed9d46a8c886d84d3189d129","tid":41741,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"快啲睇醫生拎傷殘證啦 可以去海洋公園免費入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b91aada1fb659451ab7f7837c142f7a32f8dab","tid":41741,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲睇醫生拎傷殘證啦 可以去海洋公園免費入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class